original_title: ハートキャッチプリキュア! ミュージカルショー
overview: Precure travel back to the Edo period to protect the tree of hearts from Dr. Sabark! What is the fate of Dark Precure and Precure fighting the desert apostles in the town of Edo? Everyone's energetic heart flowers call a miracle to Precure!
title: Heartcatch Precure! Musical Show
